                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>As the garrison's numbers dwindle, gold defenders melt away into worthless slag. Every time that the garrison is reduced to a threshold, it leaves behind a @Template[type:burst|distance:10]{10-foot radius} cloud of fumes and a 10-foot radius puddle of molten metal. Creatures that breathe fumes are exposed to gold defender poison. Creatures that move through the puddle take [[/r 10d6[fire]]] damage. The fumes dissipate after 1 round and the puddle completely evaporates after 1 minute.</p>"
                },
