                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Any @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained} value from this poison is reduced by 1 every hour</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:33]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 4 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r 2d6[poison]]] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r 4d6[poison]]] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r 8d6[poison]]] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 3} (1 round).</p>"
