                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> to <span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> actions</p>\n<strong>Frequency</strong> once per round\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The garrison makes a melee attack against each enemy within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:30|basic:true] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> [[/r (2d8+2)[bludgeoning]]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> [[/r (3d8+12)[bludgeoning]]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> [[/r (4d8+15)[bludgeoning]]] damage</p>"
